text: Irina Sandalova (; born 17 February 1992) is a Kazakhstani footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Kazakhstan women's national team. ==Career== Sandalova has been capped for the Kazakhstan national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani women's footballers Category:Kazakhstan women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers
